FBIS4-32053 "dreeu118_p_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-118 Daily Report 18 Jun 1994 POLAND Strike at Katowice Steelworks Suspended Strike at Katowice Steelworks Suspended LD1806080094 Warsaw PAP in Polish 0635 GMT 18 Jun 94 LD1806080094 Warsaw PAP Polish BFN [Text] Katowice, 18 Jun--The strike at Katowice Steelworks, which has been in effect since 1 June, was suspended this morning. The suspension will be in force until all demands are met and a new pay agreement coordinated, Mariusz Kwasniowski, of the steelworks' information office, reports. He added that as agreed between the strike committee and the management, each worker will get a pay raise of 1.5 million zlotys gross per month, with effect from 1 May.
